feedback_csat_explanation: The UI for SCC is not very user friendly or intuitive and thus it was difficult to search for what links or buttons I needed to click. The training could help by providing video clips of how to locate the button or link in question, for example in one of the findings the link I needed to edit a firewall rule was well below the fold on the lightbox UI.
feedback_csat_open_feedback: I learn best by doing, so I would have preferred the entire education be primarily within a lab environment so that I reinforced what I was doing by actually executing tasks. Perhaps allow an option for learners so we can specify the degree to which we want our education/experience to be via lab interaction (100% for me).
